程序包 aquintos.ee.metric.temp.calc.B_Team_Dev.VCUtil

类 VCUtil.AttributeDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • aquintos.ee.metric.temp.calc.B_Team_Dev.VCUtil.VCUtil.AttributeDefinition
  • 封闭类:
    VCUtil
    public static class VCUtil.AttributeDefinition
extends java.lang.Object
    This utility class provides methods for getting and setting attribute values in MDF objects.

    Example usage: 

     {
   @code
   // Assuming inputObject is an instance of MDFObject and attributeName is the name of the attribute
   // Get string attribute value
   String stringValue = VCUtil.AttributeDefinition.getStringAttributeValue(inputObject, attributeName);
 
   // Get boolean attribute value
   boolean booleanValue = VCUtil.AttributeDefinition.getBooleanAttributeValue(inputObject, attributeName);
 
   // Set string attribute value
   VCUtil.AttributeDefinition.setStringAttributeValue(inputObject, "new value", attributeName);
 
   // Set boolean attribute value
   VCUtil.AttributeDefinition.setBooleanAttributeValue(inputObject, true, attributeName);
 }
